  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-fa17b219-7fff-63f7-e5cf-05a166d70428&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The information submitted is of insufficient quality, accuracy, and/or lacking in clarity and content to be able to make an accurate assessment in terms of the proposed impact on the conservation area and residential amenities.&amp;nbsp; In the absence of a comprehensive Heritage Statement and acoustic and odour report, officers are unable to make an accurate assessment of the proposal&#x27;s impact on the designated heritage asset and residential amenities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 5.75pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The alterations to the shopfront, by reason of its detailed design and inappropriate materials, and the installation of the flue, by reason of its size, height, and location, visible from Stoke Newington Church Street and Lordship Road, fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the conservation area. The proposed development would fail to be in accordance with Section 72 of the Planning (Listed Buildings and Conservation Areas) Act 1990, policy HC1 of The London Plan (2021),&amp;nbsp; policy LP1, LP3 and LP4 of the Hackney Local Plan 2033, Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Alterations SPD (2009) and Hackney&#x27;s Shopfront Design Guide (Undated).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-4cd77d59-7fff-f7a6-3605-db7dcb2729fc&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;In the absence of a comprehensive acoustic and odour report, officers are unabl&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;e to make an accurate assessment in terms of the potential impacts of noise and disturbance, and fumes and odours on the residential amenities.&amp;nbsp; The proposed development would therefore fail to be in accordance with policy LP2 of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
